data.description: Welcome to Royal Highlands, where you can experience the best of Nature Coast living! We invite you to see this stunning half-acre property with a new, white vinyl fenced backyard that is perfect for any family. This freshly painted 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is move-in ready and boasts new waterproof vinyl plank tile throughout, updated appliances in the completely renovated kitchen, and remodeled bathrooms.The home also features a new well tank with added gauge ('22), UV light added ('15), and roof that was replaced in 2015. You'll find ceiling fans throughout, kitchen LEDs, and an electric fireplace in the bedroom, making this home comfortable and energy efficient. The property is beautifully landscaped with palm trees, pomegranate, peach, and red grapefruit trees. You'll love the raised bed garden, which can remain or be easily removed. There are no HOA fees or CDD fees, so you can enjoy your home without any additional costs.This home is perfect for those who want to enjoy the privacy and quiet of being in a more rural location, but just a few minutes away from the best restaurants in the area. Conveniently located near Tampa, Orlando, and Ocala, making it easy to explore all the beauty that Nature Coast has to offer. You'll be just half an hour away from the Withlacoochee Trail and only 6 miles from the Suncoast-50 trail head. And if you're looking for a fun activity, the world-renowned Weeki Wachee Springs is just a few minutes away.Don't miss the chance to see this newly listed home. Set your appointment today and start living the Nature Coast lifestyle in comfort and style!
